snippet.title: I Wanna Be A Game Dev! | Trailer 2
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2953510/I_Wanna_Be_A_Game_Dev/

"I Wanna Be A Game Dev!" is a super cute visual novel/life sim where you live our your final school days making games with your friends! Play minigames, form relationships, and get through classes on your way to make something unforgettable.
